To launch this test case:
* compile this test case
* put the Virgo <policy-management-1244>.plan on Virgo "pickup" directory
* don't forget to add the xc.properties on Virgo "pickup" directory
* start Openfire
* start Virgo
* put the Virgo <policy-management-1244>.test.plan on Virgo "pickup" directory
* Follow the tag [#1244] on the log